年的准确反映。”</p><p>麦莉·赛勒斯（Miley Cyrus）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-explores-her-deep-connection-to-fashion-on-explosive-single-something-beautiful-3850724">在爆炸性单曲“美丽的东西”上“探索她与时尚的深厚联系”</a> 。</p> ;
